Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
| **guid** | _uuid_ | Unique identifier for the role |
| **created_at** | _[timestamp](#timestamps)_ | The time with zone when the role was created|
| **updated_at**  | _[timestamp](#timestamps)_ | The time with zone when the role was last updated |
| **type** | _string_ | Role type; see [Valid role types](#valid-role-types)
| **relationships.user** | [_to-one relationship_](#to-one-relationships) | A relationship to the user; this is the user that has the role |
| **relationships.space** | [_to-one relationship_](#to-one-relationships) | A relationship to the space the role controls access to; when this is an organization role, `space.data` will be `null` |
| **relationships.organization** | [_to-one relationship_](#to-one-relationships) | A relationship to the organization the role controls access to; when this is a space role, `organization.data` will be `null` |
| **links** | [_links object_](#links) | Links to related resources |
